-- Sasol Antitrust Settlement Agreement to Face Objections From Omnia, AECI
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-13T11:09:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/sasol-antitrust-settlement-agreement-to-face-objections-from-omnia-aeci.html

          
          
             Sasol Ltd.’s settlement agreement
with South Africa’s Competition Commission for abusing its
position in the fertilizer market will face objections from AECI
Ltd.’s Africa Explosives unit and Omnia Holdings Ltd., the
antitrust regulator said.  
 The objections will be heard at a Competition Tribunal
hearing tomorrow, the Pretoria-based regulator said in an e-
mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        